snippet.title: 7 Billion Humans - Official Nintendo Switch Trailer - launching OCTOBER 25
snippet.description:
Official Nintendo Switch trailer for 7 Billion Humans. Arriving on the Nintendo eShop Thursday, October 25. Pre-purchase begins one week early on Thursday, October 18.

Automate swarms of office workers to solve puzzles inside your very own parallel computer made of people. ...a thrilling followup to the award winning Human Resource Machine. Now with more humans! 

http://tomorrowcorporation.com
